    @FunctionalInterface
public interface FloatOperator1
extends OperatorN<java.lang.Float>, net.ashwork.functionality.primitive.floats.ToFloatFunctionN, net.ashwork.functionality.partial.InputChainableInput<java.lang.Float>, net.ashwork.functionality.partial.UnboxedAll<Operator1<java.lang.Float>,net.ashwork.functionality.primitive.floats.ToFloatFunction1<java.lang.Float>,net.ashwork.functionality.primitive.floats.FloatFunction1<java.lang.Float>>
    Represents an operation that accepts a float-valued operand and produces a result of the same type as its operand. This is the one-arity specialization of OperatorN. This is the float-consuming primitive specialization of ToFloatFunction1. This is the float-producing primitive specialization of FloatFunction1.

    This is a functional interface whose functional method is applyAsFloat(float).
